        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【评测】DJI Goggles N3，价格亲民 + FPV 入门不错选择</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/12/dji-goggles-n3/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dji-goggles-n3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/12/dji-goggles-n3/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 04:30:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[dji]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[DJI Neo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[drone]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1274292</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>自从 DJI Neo 推出后，市场上便迎来了一波航拍机的热潮。与传统航拍机相比，DJI Neo 以其低廉的售价（HK$1,399）以及极其便捷的操控方式，迅速吸引了众多消费者的目光。而其重量更只是 135g，香港航拍法已生效，它就成为一部不用实名登记及买保险，便可以立即上手玩的航拍机，自然吸引了大量的香港用家及新手入坑了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274308" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_1090-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_1090-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_1090.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>今次 DJI 继续看准 DJI Neo 的市场，为它推出一副可说专为 DJI Neo 而设的 DJI Goggles N3，能令用家体验到 FPV 飞行的同时，也将定位价格压得更低，成为了许多人入门 FPV 飞行的好选择。</p><h2>价格亲民打破高门槛</h2><p>过去，如果你想体验 FPV 飞行，必须购买价位不菲的装备。例如之前 DJI Neo 要配上 Goggles 3，这部高阶的眼罩需要 HK $3,869 的价钱，这对于很多用户来说是一个不小的负担，尤其是当 DJI Neo 本身的价格本身已经很低廉时，一部千多元的航拍机要配一副 3 千尾的眼罩？很难吸引到 Neo 用家去购买的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274294" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snap0533-694x290.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="290" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snap0533-694x290.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snap0533.jpg 1258w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>现在 DJI 在新眼罩 Goggles N3 上做出了显著的价格定位，将价格定在 HK $1,669 ，让更多人能够以更低的成本，享受到先进的 FPV 体验。与同类型的 FPV 眼镜相比，Goggles N3 以其极高的性价比，吸引了大量对 FPV 飞行感兴趣，但又不愿意花费过多的消费者。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274296" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snap0534-694x317.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="317" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snap0534-694x317.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/snap0534.jpg 1251w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>戴眼镜也可轻松使用</h2><p>Goggles N3 在设计上比 Goggles 3 进行了优化，最大的改变便是它更大的尺寸和舒适度。这款眼镜的内部空间比起 Goggles 3 宽敞许多，长时间佩戴后的舒适度也得到了显著提升。过去，如果你戴著眼镜很难用到 Goggles 3 的，会发现眼镜无法与眼罩完全适配，或者要除下眼镜才能戴到 Goggles 3。如今新的 Goggles N3 设计解决了这一问题，眼罩的深度足够容纳大多数眼镜，戴眼镜人士可以轻松使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274318" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4765-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4765-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4765.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲眼罩的深度足够容纳大多数眼镜</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274301" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4449-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4449-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4449.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小编是四眼肥仔一名，戴著眼镜再配戴 DJI Goggles N3 时，没有感到不适或不便，眼镜的位置也刚刚好。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274302" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4456-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4456-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4456.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲虽然 Goggles N3 比 Goggles 3 较为重，但小编的女友配戴 Goggles N3 时，也不会觉得太重感觉，重量是可接受程度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274319" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4760-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4760-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4760.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲右边的 Power 掣</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4761-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4761-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4761.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲右方顶部设有十字掣及 Back 掣</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274321" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4762-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4762-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4762.jpg 675w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机顶可插 Micro SD 卡录影</p><p>此外，N3 的调整设计更加人性化。过去的 Goggles 系列需要使用者进行镜片对焦的调整，这个过程相当繁琐，并且即使调整好了，还会因为头部微小的移动而影响视觉焦距。而 N3 删除了这一设计，采用了一个固定的 3.5 吋大屏幕，如有戴眼镜的照戴著眼镜，直接佩戴 Goggles N3 后即可呈现清晰的画面，减少了过去繁琐的调整视距步骤。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274309 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dji_20241106142742_0-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dji_20241106142742_0-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dji_20241106142742_0.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用 DJI Neo 作航拍时，紧记留意余下电量，以及大风就勿飞了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274314" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4758-694x478.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="478" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4758-694x478.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4758.jpg 1164w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲眼镜内亦可自行录影</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274315" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4757-694x377.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4757-694x377.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_4757.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲眼镜画面亦有增稳选项</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/12/dji-goggles-n3/review-2/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
